.SH "NAME"
Data::Perl::Role::Counter \- Wrapping class for a simple numeric counter.
.SH "VERSION"
.IX Header "VERSION"
version 0.002011
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\&  use Data::Perl qw/counter/;
\&
\&  my $c = counter(4);
\&
\&  $c\->inc;   # $c == 5
\&
\&  $c\->reset; # $c == 0
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This class provides a wrapper and methods for a simple numeric counter.
